   The sign for hippie uses a "bent-4" handshape.  The fingers can 
			be thought of as representing the "long hair" worn by hippies.
   <br/>
   Aim the "hair" a bit back and then "swing" it forward. Do this 
			movement twice as if showing how a hippie's hair might swing back 
			and forth.
   <br/>
